message_1: What is the rank of the rank 2 vector bundle over the real projective plane $\mathbb{RP}^2$ with Euler class 3?
message_2: The rank of a vector bundle is the dimension of its fibers. In this case, the problem states that the vector bundle has rank 2. Therefore, the rank of the vector bundle over the real projective plane $\mathbb{RP}^2$ with Euler class 3 is 2.
